# [pyfunc2](http://lib.pyfunc.com)

libs for cameramonit, ocr, fin-officer, cfo, and other projects


## Install


```bash
pip install pyfunc2
```

```bash
git clone https://github.com/pyfunc/lib.git pyfunc
```


